{"tid":437001,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"首爾旅行求解答","createTime":"2017-10-15T15:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T08:14:58.000Z","uid":136910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84d22e6b67d580df0037c0248197e337bd8c4034","tid":437001,"uid":136910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"plan緊冬天sem break去首爾，兩個人5-6日（可能去下周邊)唔計機票酒店大概要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身份人唔大洗但係對食有少少要求"},{"pid":"2da3a1010b66c8bccbcca91413211a0d9dcf33db","tid":437001,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"無地方好去 去日本好過<br />\n利申 留學撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc7015732abe557deb55f5299b2fa5208906c5b","tid":437001,"uid":69049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"淨食既話2-3000港紙都好夠<br />\n果邊食物一般唔算好貴 咁當然貴有貴食啦<br />\n巴打冬天去6日可以join滑雪團喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋南怡島都好靚 不過地下全部都係雪/結冰好跣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261004ddcff5c6843f8091979a8ca836dc4d5ddd","tid":437001,"uid":137293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"我前排去過 係個度洗最多都係買衫<br />\n你有無搵過一間叫ashley 係自助餐黎架 我覺得平得黎都算幾好食 我去過兩次韓國兩次都有食<br />\n睇你想食咩啦 你普通韓燒都係萬零won 有啲韓牛個啲哥能就貴啲<br />\n其實我去咁耐食得最貴都係每人二萬won樓下咋<br />\n不過講真韓國真係有啲悶如果唔係中意買野 不過你冬天去可以睇雪一定仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望幫到你啦!"},{"pid":"5fc304e78768e683fda54534db3a50e33eabbc18","tid":437001,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"7703446037a34c1f1e90be7b771fadd40168a275","tid":437001,"uid":104383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"你預食晒d米芝蓮咩醬油蝦蟹，豬肉，1++韓牛，人參雞，炸雞，豬腳就4000到啦，但真心，再貴都係垃圾"},{"pid":"a679491e3b875c26d56ebd3e138acdcb05f27082","tid":437001,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:42:52.000Z","msg":"你預每餐10000won啦"},{"pid":"239a3b8ec073fd438a6f29aa7502309d6b87b90b","tid":437001,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:43:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家唔去好過去"},{"pid":"9b86ae6c7d257deef8dbf7a1c8694f0c1accd56b","tid":437001,"uid":136910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}